<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Hi.</p>

<p>When iterating Zend_Pagination object created with Zend_Pagination_Adapter_Array which uses array:</p>

<p>array(2) {
      [127443] =&gt; string(8) "12345678"
      [1270236] =&gt; string(8) "12345678"
    }</p>

<p>array indexes are reset. In function:</p>

<p>/**
     * Returns an array of items for a page.
     *
     * @param  integer $offset Page offset
     * @param  integer $itemCountPerPage Number of items per page
     * @return array
     */
    public function getItems($offset, $itemCountPerPage)
    {
        return array_slice($this-&gt;_array, $offset, $itemCountPerPage);
    }</p>

<p>array_slice could have $preserve_keys set to true in which case indexes wouldn't be reset.</p>

